{
  "stem": "4289.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was already springtime, so the hotels were still not filled with tourists.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there was probably around 100 people there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We stayed there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the time was going by.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we stayed another week, and another week.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In about fourth week, we were taken into buses and taken on a boat, Italian boat, going to Israel.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everything was paid by Sochnut, the Jewish organizations that help.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we came on a boat, very, very hard part of the voyage.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the sea was very, you know--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rough.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And everybody got sick on the boat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They couldn't eat.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Me and my father were the only ones in the restaurant coming every day to eat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the first time I got to taste the olives, the pickled olives.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Which I said, how can people eat this?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is terrible!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I spit it out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I came to Israel, finally, I learned to love it, that food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But coming to Israel, finally, we arrived to the port of Haifa.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was so excited to see beautiful buildings from far.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It didn't look anything like those postcards we got from, you know, Israel during the New Year's, where a camel was walking with a Arab or something like that, in a big Negev or whatever.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I saw those beautiful buildings and stores right there, I was very excited.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It looked to me a little bit like Vienna.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And while my folks, my parents, were arranging things to move on and take in the luggage and everything, I was sent to meet my uncle, [NON-ENGLISH], my father's brother, and his wife.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She came.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was released right away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the aunt gave me address where to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She lived only two streets away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they went to pick up their children.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
